title: 3D elevation
name: 3D elevation
description: This globe presents elevation data at approximately 90m or 1km per pixel resolution for the world. The elevation data includes 90m Shuttle Radar Topography Mission (SRTM) elevation data from NASA and National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA) where it is available and 1km GTOPO30 data from the USGS elsewhere. Vertical units are measured in meters.
